258
00:17:24,160 --> 00:17:26,200
Hello, Reeny girl, how are you going?

259
00:17:26,400 --> 00:17:30,000
- I thought you went down with the Lusitania.
- Fiver says he did.

260
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:35,600
