276
00:18:40,920 --> 00:18:44,880
Oh, yeah, me and Joannie, the terrible twins.

277
00:18:46,080 --> 00:18:49,520
Do you remember when your mum had
that cleaning job down at the town hall?

278
00:18:49,720 --> 00:18:51,160
