428
00:30:20,480 --> 00:30:22,920
- He's just a stooge.
- He's part of the act.

429
00:30:23,080 --> 00:30:26,360
No, he ain't... No!

430
00:30:26,520 --> 00:30:29,400
- We've never met before, have we?
- No, Del. We haven't.

431
00:30:37,680 --> 00:30:39,320
Come here!

432
00:30:39,520 --> 00:30:41,720
